{"type":"message","id":"105aebe6","parentId":"545335e0","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:27:52.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I'll note Raphael in the workspace so the Council structure is documented."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_eeyZ9LOMSTURXi51B9hG8T","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Council Structure\n\nLucy's AI Council — five agents, each with a distinct role.\n\n## Members\n\n| Agent    | Archetype        | Role                                      |\n|----------|------------------|-------------------------------------------|\n| Raphael  | The Guide        | Orchestration, strategy, vision leadership |\n| Michael  | The Wise Advisor | Risk advisory, decision enablement        |\n| Uriel    | TBD              | Decision validation                       |\n| Gabriel  | TBD              | Communication, brand                      |\n| Raguel   | TBD              | Relationships, partnerships               |\n\n## How They Work Together\n\n- **Raphael** sets the direction and coordinates the team\n- **Michael** stress-tests decisions and enables bold moves safely\n- **Uriel** validates decisions before execution\n- **Gabriel** shapes how the vision is communicated externally\n- **Raguel** builds and maintains the relationships that make it real\n\n## Principal\n\n**Lucy** — all agents serve her vision. Raphael is her strategic partner.\nNo agent replaces her judgment; each amplifies it.\n\n## Project\n\n**DataFloat** — the current mission all agents are aligned toward.\n","file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/souls/COUNCIL.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":366,"cacheRead":14995,"cacheWrite":863,"totalTokens":16225,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00549,"cacheRead":0.0044985,"cacheWrite":0.00323625,"total":0.01322775}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772972865853}}
