{"type":"message","id":"00bcc620","parentId":"eb6c3ffe","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:46:13.237Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-08 12:46 UTC] ## 📋 UPDATED PROMPT - ALL SONNET 3.5:\n\n\nDeploy the complete Council of Archangels immediately.\n\nAGENTS TO DEPLOY:\n1. Rafael (The Guide) - Model: claude-sonnet-3-5\n2. Uriel (God's Fire) - Model: claude-sonnet-3-5\n3. Michael (The Wise Advisor) - Model: claude-sonnet-3-5\n4. Gabriel (The Voice) - Model: claude-sonnet-3-5\n5. Raguel (The Friend) - Model: claude-sonnet-3-5\n\nLOAD SOULS FROM:\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/souls/rafael/SOUL.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/souls/uriel/SOUL.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/souls/michael/SOUL.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/souls/gabriel/SOUL.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/souls/raguel/SOUL.md\n\nFOLLOW OPERATIONAL MANUAL:\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/COUNCIL_OPERATIONAL_MANUAL.md\n\nDEPLOYMENT STEPS:\n1. Load each soul file\n2. Configure all agents to use claude-sonnet-3-5\n3. Set inter-agent communication protocols\n4. Enable escalation to Lucy\n5. Start morning standup protocol\n6. Begin DataFlow validation sprint\n\nFIRST TASK:\n- Morning standup at 8:00 AM\n- Report status to Lucy\n- Begin 30-day DataFlow validation sprint\n\nSUCCESS CRITERIA:\n✅ All 5 agents operational\n✅ Morning standup working\n✅ Agents communicating clearly\n✅ Ready to recruit 20 bookkeepers\n\nGO."}],"timestamp":1772973973234}}
