{"type":"message","id":"62751204","parentId":"a169e943","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:48:05.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me initialize the DataFloat sprint tracker:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_zVCQ5F6xxNcUKf53bxHUXF","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# DataFloat — 30-Day Validation Sprint\n\n**Start Date:** 2026-03-08\n**End Date:** 2026-04-07\n**Goal:** 20 bookkeepers committed to DataFloat validation\n\n## Sprint Status\n\n| Week | Target               | Status  |\n|------|----------------------|---------|\n| 1    | Foundation + 5 leads | 🔵 Active |\n| 2    | Pipeline + 10 convos | ⚪ Pending |\n| 3    | 10+ qualified        | ⚪ Pending |\n| 4    | 20 committed         | ⚪ Pending |\n\n## Bookkeeper Pipeline\n\nSee: `datafloat/pipeline.md`\n\n## This Week's Focus (Week 1)\n\n- [ ] Rafael: Define success metrics and targets\n- [ ] Uriel: Research ideal bookkeeper profile\n- [ ] Michael: Risk-assess outreach approach\n- [ ] Gabriel: Draft outreach messaging\n- [ ] Raguel: Identify first 5 prospects and begin warm outreach\n\n## Notes\n\n_Updated weekly by Rafael. Logged daily in memory/._\n","file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/datafloat/SPRINT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_WS8VHdJCQggweehdrkKSjQ","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Bookkeeper Pipeline\n\n**Goal:** 20 committed bookkeepers by 2026-04-07\n\n## Pipeline Stages\n\n| Stage        | Description                              | Count |\n|--------------|------------------------------------------|-------|\n| Identified   | Prospect found, not yet contacted        | 0     |\n| Contacted    | Outreach sent                            | 0     |\n| Conversation | In active dialogue                       | 0     |\n| Qualified    | Confirmed fit, interest high             | 0     |\n| Committed    | Agreed to validate DataFloat             | 0     |\n\n## Prospects\n\n_Raguel to populate as outreach begins._\n\n| Name | Business | Stage | Contact | Notes |\n|------|----------|-------|---------|-------|\n|      |          |       |         |       |\n\n## Ideal Bookkeeper Profile\n\n_Uriel to complete during Week 1 research._\n\n- Business type: TBD\n- Firm size: TBD\n- Tech comfort: TBD\n- Pain points: TBD\n","file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/datafloat/pipeline.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":677,"cacheRead":20945,"cacheWrite":1749,"totalTokens":23372,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.010155,"cacheRead":0.0062835,"cacheWrite":0.00655875,"total":0.02300025}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772974074655}}
