{"type":"message","id":"c4c094a4","parentId":"6f330321","timestamp":"2026-03-08T12:48:13.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Workspace is fully built. Here's the status:\n\n**✅ Soul files created:**\n- `souls/rafael/SOUL.md` — The Guide\n- `souls/uriel/SOUL.md` — God's Fire\n- `souls/michael/SOUL.md` — The Wise Advisor\n- `souls/gabriel/SOUL.md` — The Voice\n- `souls/raguel/SOUL.md` — The Friend\n\n**✅ Operational infrastructure:**\n- `COUNCIL_OPERATIONAL_MANUAL.md` — full playbook, standup rhythm, escalation, decision flow\n- `datafloat/SPRINT.md` — 30-day sprint tracker, week-by-week targets\n- `datafloat/pipeline.md` — bookkeeper pipeline, stages, ideal profile (Uriel to fill in Week 1)\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ One honest flag (Michael speaking):**\nI can't run `openclaw` commands from inside the sandbox — the CLI lives on your host. To actually deploy the 4 additional agents, you'll need to run the agent creation commands on the VPS itself.\n\n**Run `openclaw agent --help` on your VPS** and paste the output here — I'll give you the exact commands to spin up all 5 agents with the right models and soul files.\n\nEverything else is ready to go the moment they're deployed. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":331,"cacheRead":22694,"cacheWrite":787,"totalTokens":23813,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.004965,"cacheRead":0.0068081999999999995,"cacheWrite":0.00295125,"total":0.01472745}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772974086366}}
