{"type":"message","id":"7223fbe3","parentId":"8f62f284","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:00:45.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] The Council is live. 🛡️🧭🔥📣🤝\n\n**All 5 agents operational:**\n| Agent | Identity | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| 🛡️ Michael | The Wise Advisor | `main` (you're talking to me now) |\n| 🧭 Rafael | The Guide | ✅ Deployed |\n| 🔥 Uriel | God's Fire | ✅ Deployed |\n| 📣 Gabriel | The Voice | ✅ Deployed |\n| 🤝 Raguel | The Friend | ✅ Deployed |\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ One flag:** Claude Sonnet 3.5 isn't configured on this system — only **Sonnet 4.6** (via AWS Bedrock) is available. All agents are running on that. If you want Sonnet 3.5, you'd need to add an Anthropic API key via `openclaw configure`.\n\n---\n\n**Next steps to complete the sprint launch:**\n\n1. **Morning standup cron** — want me to set up an 8:00 AM daily standup? I'll need your timezone.\n2. **Test the agents** — say the word and I'll ping Rafael for a Council intro\n3. **Bookkeeper profile** — Uriel should define the ideal profile so Raguel knows who to target\n\nWhat do you want to do first?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":345,"cacheRead":39833,"cacheWrite":524,"totalTokens":40703,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.005175,"cacheRead":0.0119499,"cacheWrite":0.001965,"total":0.019092900000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772974836911}}
