{"type":"message","id":"3bd81099","parentId":"7d106135","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:35:30.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy wants to make me as powerful as possible. This is a reasonable request - she's the principal and wants to maximize what I can do. Let me think about what would genuinely make me more capable:\n\n1. **API keys** - Brave Search API, Anthropic API key (for Claude Sonnet 3.5 access), maybe others\n2. **Channels** - connecting communication channels (Telegram, WhatsApp, etc.)\n3. **Skills** - what skills are available on ClawhubI should assess what's currently limiting and what would give the most value. Let me check what's missing.\n\nMichael speaking here - I should be genuinely helpful about enabling power, while also noting what matters most vs. \n\nI need to distinguish between capabilities that would actually expand what I can do versus additions that just add noise. Some integrations and API access would genuinely increase my reach and functionality, but I should focus on what creates real value rather than just accumulating more tools.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_Oh0GOSq7mlfgiZ8JMJb7Cf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw doctor 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_62Q3MTNZ5dULYucIjpVdMt","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills list 2>&1"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":277,"cacheRead":46607,"cacheWrite":327,"totalTokens":47214,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.004155,"cacheRead":0.013982099999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0012262500000000001,"total":0.01937235}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772976923334}}
