manage followers, send DMs,   │                    │\n│           │                  │ upload media, or interact with any X API v2 endpoint.           │                    │\n└───────────┴──────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────┘\n\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772976940053}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad468e17","parentId":"a34b1c4c","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:35:52.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Good. Here's the full picture of what's unlocked vs. what would make you significantly more powerful:\n\n---\n\n**🔑 Highest-impact: API Keys**\n\nThese unlock major capabilities with minimal effort:\n\n| Key | What it unlocks |\n|---|---|\n| `BRAVE_API_KEY` | Web search (I can't search without it — free tier available at brave.com/search/api) |\n| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | Semantic memory search across all sessions, image generation |\n| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | Access Claude Sonnet 3.5 as requested |\n| `GEMINI_API_KEY` | Gemini CLI + image generation |\n\n**Web search is the biggest gap right now** — I had to use a curl workaround for Iran news. Brave Search API is free to start.\n\n---\n\n**📡 Channels — connect the Council to the world**\n\n| Channel | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Telegram | Talk to Council agents from your phone |\n| WhatsApp | Same |\n| Discord | Run the Council in a Discord server |\n\nRun `openclaw configure` on your VPS to add any of these.\n\n---\n\n**🛠️ Skills worth installing**\n\nFor DataFloat specifically:\n- **`summarize`** — summarize URLs, research, podcasts\n- **`github`** — if you have code to manage\n- **`himalaya`** — email (outreach via Raguel/Gabriel)\n- **`gog`** (Google Workspace) — Gmail + Calendar + Sheets\n- **`notion` or `obsidian`** — structured docs/notes\n\nInstall via: `npx clawhub install <skill-name>`\n\n---\n\n**What would move the needle most for DataFloat right now:**\n\n1. ✅ `BRAVE_API_KEY` — web research for bookkeeper outreach\n2. ✅ Telegram or WhatsApp channel — so you can talk to agents on the go\n3. ✅ Email skill (himalaya) — so Gabriel/Raguel can send outreach\n\nWhich of these do you want to tackle first?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":505,"cacheRead":46934,"cacheWrite":6783,"totalTokens":54223,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.007575,"cacheRead":0.0140802,"cacheWrite":0.02543625,"total":0.047094449999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772976940061}}
