{"type":"message","id":"106e325a","parentId":"2d63dca3","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:37:12.170Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is offering to give me a Google account. This could be useful for:\n1. Google search (alternative to Brave)\n2. Gmail for outreach\n3. Google Workspace (gog skill)\n4. Gemini API\n\nI should clarify what she means - does she want to give me credentials to an existing Google account, or create a new one? And what does she want me to use it for?\n\nI should be careful here - if she gives me Google account credentials, I can use them for various things. I should clarify the intent and note the security implications.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] That works — a Google account opens up a lot.\n\n**What I can do with it:**\n- 📧 **Gmail** — Gabriel/Raguel can send outreach emails\n- 📅 **Google Calendar** — scheduling, standup reminders\n- 📊 **Google Sheets** — track the bookkeeper pipeline\n- 🔍 **Google search** (via Gemini/custom search API)\n- 🤖 **Gemini API** — alternative AI model + image generation\n\n**How to share it safely:**\nDon't paste credentials directly in chat. Instead, on your VPS run:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw configure --section model\n```\n\nOr set environment variables:\n```bash\nopenclaw config set auth.google.email \"your@gmail.com\"\nopenclaw config set auth.google.password \"yourpassword\"\n```\n\nActually — the best way depends on what you want to use it for. **Is this a dedicated account for the Council, or your personal Google account?**\n\nIf it's dedicated (recommended), share the email + app password here and I'll configure it properly. A dedicated account is safer — the Council operates from it without touching your personal stuff."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":418,"cacheRead":54295,"cacheWrite":284,"totalTokens":55000,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.00627,"cacheRead":0.0162885,"cacheWrite":0.001065,"total":0.0236325}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772977022897}}
