{"type":"message","id":"ca113dab","parentId":"37409bd4","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:49:44.487Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Ah — they changed it. No more free tier, it's pay-as-you-go now.\n\n**Good news though:** it includes **$5 free credits every month** automatically. At $5/1,000 requests that's 1,000 free searches/month — plenty for the Council.\n\nYou're already logged into the dashboard. Just:\n1. Click **\"API Keys\"** in the left sidebar\n2. Create a key\n3. Paste it here — I'll configure it on the VPS immediately\n\nThe $5 monthly credit covers normal usage without paying anything extra."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":141,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":56612,"totalTokens":56756,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.002115,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.212295,"total":0.214419}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772977777357}}
