{"type":"message","id":"bf5d09c4","parentId":"6bf06a21","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:50:09.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy wants free alternatives to Brave Search API. Let me think about what's available:\n\n1. **DuckDuckGo** - has an unofficial API (no key needed, but limited)\n2. **SerpAPI** - has a free tier (100 searches/month)\n3. **Google Custom Search** - 100 queries/day free\n4. **Tavily** - has a free tier (1000 credits/month)\n5. **Serper.dev** - 2500 free searches on signup\n6. **Bing Search API** - Azure, has some free tier\n\nFor the Council's purposes, let me think about what's most useful and actually free:\n\n\nSerper.dev gives the most upfront with 2,500 free searches, while Tavily offers 1,000 monthly and Google Custom Search provides 100 daily. But I could also just use curl to fetch web content directly for specific URLs, or pull from Google News RSS feeds like I've done before. Let me recommend the best combination of these options.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Yes — a few good options:\n\n**Best free alternatives:**\n\n| Service | Free Tier | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Serper.dev** | 2,500 searches free (one-time) | Google results, no card needed |\n| **Tavily** | 1,000/month free | Built for AI agents, great quality |\n| **Google Custom Search** | 100/day free | Needs Google account you already have |\n| **SerpAPI** | 100/month free | Generous but low volume |\n\n**My recommendation: Tavily** — it's designed specifically for AI agents, 1,000/month free, no credit card. Sign up at **https://tavily.com**\n\n**Or — I already have a workaround.** I used RSS feeds + curl to pull the Iran news. I can do the same for most research tasks without any API key. It's not as clean as a proper search API but it works for free right now.\n\nWant me to:\n1. Set up the curl/RSS workaround immediately so we have search-like capability now\n2. Wait while you grab a Tavily key (2 minutes, free)\n3. Use your Google account for Google Custom Search\n\nWhat's easiest for you?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":586,"cacheRead":54579,"cacheWrite":697,"totalTokens":55865,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.008790000000000001,"cacheRead":0.016373699999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00261375,"total":0.02778645}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772977796544}}
