{"type":"message","id":"b56765a4","parentId":"6b22223c","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:52:56.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_OuCrRTDgQqecNChgGI9YG9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/bin && cat > ~/bin/search << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\nQUERY=\"$*\"\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://api.tavily.com/search\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d \"{\\\"api_key\\\":\\\"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\\\",\\\"query\\\":\\\"$(echo $QUERY | sed 's/\"/\\\\\"/g')\\\",\\\"max_results\\\":5}\" | \\\n  python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor r in d.get('results', []):\n    print(f\\\"## {r['title']}\\\")\n    print(f\\\"URL: {r['url']}\\\")\n    print(f\\\"{r.get('content','')[:300]}\\\")\n    print()\n\"\nEOF\nchmod +x ~/bin/search\n\n# Test it\n~/bin/search \"DataFloat bookkeeping software\" 2>&1 | head -20"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":331,"cacheRead":58431,"cacheWrite":442,"totalTokens":59205,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.004965,"cacheRead":0.017529299999999998,"cacheWrite":0.0016575000000000001,"total":0.024154799999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772977972104}}
{"type":"message","id":"a8afcdce","parentId":"b56765a4","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:52:57.083Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_OuCrRTDgQqecNChgGI9YG9","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Faster Month-end with Accounting Automations & Bookkeeping - Float\nURL: https://floatfinancial.com/platform/accounting-automations/\nSave time by exporting transactions already coded and with receipts. Float’s Bill Pay product helps businesses of all sizes automate Accounts Payable and streamlines AP by integrating AI-powered document extraction, custom approval workflows, and seamless payment methods like EFT, ACH, and Global Wi\n\n## Which accounting software tools does Float integrate with?\nURL: https://help.floatfinancial.com/hc/en-us/articles/4408675553428-Which-accounting-software-tools-does-Float-integrate-with\nFloat has direct integrations with: QuickBooks Online (QBO), Xero and NetSuite. If you are using another accounting software (eg.\n\n## 20+ Best Bookkeeping Software for Businesses (2026 Tool Guide)\nURL: https://pilot.com/blog/bookkeeping-software-for-business\nBookkeeping software helps a business owner or bookkeeper manage that data. For example, many bookkeeping software tools can connect seamlessly with your bank account to import transactions and other financial data. In short, bookkeepers will manage and record the financial information of a business\n\n## Cash flow budgeting using float app - Meru Accounting\nURL: https://www.meruaccounting.com/cash-flow-budgeting-using-float-app/\n# **How to Manage Your Finances Using Float Cash Flow Budget Software**. ## **What Is Float Cash Flow and How Does It Work?**. Float Cash Flow is a tool that helps you track and forecast your business’s income and expenses. ## **Key Features of Float Cash Flow Budget Software**. With shared float vi\n\n## How to export transactions in Float's new Accounting Hub - YouTube\nURL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9c8rSsmvXEU\nAs part of Float's upcoming Accounting Hub release, finance admins can now access the Hub's Transaction Exports page and experience"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":965,"aggregated":"## Faster Month-end with Accounting Automations & Bookkeeping - Float\nURL: https://floatfinancial.com/platform/accounting-automations/\nSave time by exporting transactions already coded and with receipts. Float’s Bill Pay product helps businesses of all sizes automate Accounts Payable and streamlines AP by integrating AI-powered document extraction, custom approval workflows, and seamless payment methods like EFT, ACH, and Global Wi\n\n## Which accounting software tools does Float integrate with?\nURL: https://help.floatfinancial.com/hc/en-us/articles/4408675553428-Which-accounting-software-tools-does-Float-integrate-with\nFloat has direct integrations with: QuickBooks Online (QBO), Xero and NetSuite. If you are using another accounting software (eg.\n\n## 20+ Best Bookkeeping Software for Businesses (2026 Tool Guide)\nURL: https://pilot.com/blog/bookkeeping-software-for-business\nBookkeeping software helps a business owner or bookkeeper manage that data. For example, many bookkeeping software tools can connect seamlessly with your bank account to import transactions and other financial data. In short, bookkeepers will manage and record the financial information of a business\n\n## Cash flow budgeting using float app - Meru Accounting\nURL: https://www.meruaccounting.com/cash-flow-budgeting-using-float-app/\n# **How to Manage Your Finances Using Float Cash Flow Budget Software**. ## **What Is Float Cash Flow and How Does It Work?**. Float Cash Flow is a tool that helps you track and forecast your business’s income and expenses. ## **Key Features of Float Cash Flow Budget Software**. With shared float vi\n\n## How to export transactions in Float's new Accounting Hub - YouTube\nURL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9c8rSsmvXEU\nAs part of Float's upcoming Accounting Hub release, finance admins can now access the Hub's Transaction Exports page and experience","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772977977079}}
{"type":"message","id":"a159fe8b","parentId":"a8afcdce","timestamp":"2026-03-08T13:53:03.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Search is working. Now let me also store the key properly for all agents and restart the gateway:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_2BWgciusOle3oLiNQlfIRZ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Store Tavily key in workspace TOOLS.md for reference\ncat >> ~/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md << 'EOF'\n\n### Search\n\n- **Provider:** Tavily (https://tavily.com)\n- **Key stored in:** `tools.web.search.apiKey` (openclaw config) + `~/bin/search` CLI wrapper\n- **Usage:** `~/bin/search \"your query\"` from any agent exec\n\n### Notes\n\n- OpenClaw native `web_search` tool requires Brave API key\n- Use `~/bin/search` or direct Tavily curl calls as the search method\nEOF\n\n# Copy search script to all agent workspaces\nfor ws in workspace-rafael workspace-uriel workspace-gabriel workspace-raguel; do\n  cp ~/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md ~/.openclaw/$ws/TOOLS.md 2>/dev/null || true\ndone\n\nopenclaw gateway restart 2>&1 | tail -5"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":292,"cacheRead":58873,"cacheWrite":814,"totalTokens":59980,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00438,"cacheRead":0.017661899999999998,"cacheWrite":0.0030525,"total":0.0250974}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772977977084}}
