{"type":"message","id":"e2de4a09","parentId":"7939d9b7","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:01:55.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The dmPolicy is \"pairing\" - which means I need to pair with Lucy's Telegram account. The groupPolicy is now \"open\" so groups work. For DMs, she needs to initiate a pairing. Let me guide her through that.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Telegram is configured and live. ✅\n\n**To connect your account:**\n\nThe bot is in **pairing mode** for DMs (secure — only paired users can chat with it).\n\n**Do this right now:**\n1. Open Telegram\n2. Search for your bot (the username you gave BotFather)\n3. Send `/start`\n4. It'll give you a pairing code — paste it here and I'll approve it\n\nThat links your Telegram account to the Council. After that you can message me (and any agent) directly from your phone.\n\nGo send `/start` to the bot! 📱"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":217,"cacheRead":64788,"cacheWrite":366,"totalTokens":65372,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.003255,"cacheRead":0.0194364,"cacheWrite":0.0013725,"total":0.0240669}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772978508190}}
