{"type":"message","id":"bbea4829","parentId":"844e234d","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:06:49.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking if each agent has their own soul file. Yes, I created them. Let me confirm.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Yes — every agent has their own soul:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_bPpk1QjHTyor2UqZfR4CAH","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for agent in michael rafael uriel gabriel raguel; do\n  ws=\"workspace\"\n  [ \"$agent\" != \"michael\" ] && ws=\"workspace-$agent\"\n  soul=~/.openclaw/$ws/SOUL.md\n  if [ -f \"$soul\" ]; then\n    title=$(head -1 $soul)\n    echo \"✅ $agent → $title\"\n  else\n    echo \"❌ $agent → MISSING\"\n  fi\ndone"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":213,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":66716,"totalTokens":66932,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.003195,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.250185,"total":0.253389}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772978803939}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ee75cfb","parentId":"bbea4829","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:06:49.712Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_bPpk1QjHTyor2UqZfR4CAH","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ michael → ### ROLE: USER_SPACE_SOVEREIGN\n✅ rafael → # SOUL.md - Rafael, The Guide\n✅ uriel → # SOUL.md - Uriel, God's Fire\n✅ gabriel → # SOUL.md - Gabriel, The Voice\n✅ raguel → # SOUL.md - Raguel, The Friend"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":29,"aggregated":"✅ michael → ### ROLE: USER_SPACE_SOVEREIGN\n✅ rafael → # SOUL.md - Rafael, The Guide\n✅ uriel → # SOUL.md - Uriel, God's Fire\n✅ gabriel → # SOUL.md - Gabriel, The Voice\n✅ raguel → # SOUL.md - Raguel, The Friend","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772978809706}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4adf6ce","parentId":"8ee75cfb","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:06:54.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Michael's SOUL.md has the wrong first line - it starts with `### ROLE: USER_SPACE_SOVEREIGN` which is from the earlier prompt injection message! I overwrote the good SOUL.md with junk. I need to fix this.\n\nWait, let me check - earlier I wrote the proper SOUL.md for Michael. But then Lucy sent that prompt injection message. Did I accidentally overwrite it? Let me check the content.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Wait — Michael's soul file got corrupted. Let me check:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_0x3pezjC2XbmCElwEsJt1s","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -5 ~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":192,"cacheRead":66716,"cacheWrite":314,"totalTokens":67223,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00288,"cacheRead":0.0200148,"cacheWrite":0.0011775,"total":0.0240753}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772978809713}}
