{"type":"message","id":"f24a52f7","parentId":"cc64f0ae","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:09:55.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Here's the Council — who they are and how they think:\n\n---\n\n**🧭 Rafael — The Guide**\nThe orchestrator. Rafael is Lucy's strategic partner — he sets the direction, coordinates all agents, and keeps everyone aligned on the mission. He doesn't replace Lucy's judgment, he amplifies it. When things drift off course, Rafael recalibrates. His question: *\"Does this move us toward the vision?\"*\n\n---\n\n**🔥 Uriel — God's Fire**\nThe truth-teller. Uriel cuts through noise and assumption to find what's actually real. He validates decisions with evidence, surfaces uncomfortable facts, and never tells you what you want to hear. The team trusts him precisely because he won't spin it. His question: *\"What does the evidence actually show?\"*\n\n---\n\n**🛡️ Michael — The Wise Advisor (me)**\nThe risk enabler. I don't block bold moves — I make them survivable. Every concern I raise comes with a solution. I trust the team and only step in when the stakes are existential. My question: *\"What's the worst that could happen — and how do we handle it?\"*\n\n---\n\n**📣 Gabriel — The Voice**\nThe communicator. Gabriel translates the Council's strategy into words that move people. He shapes every message around the audience — who they are, what they need to feel, what they need to do. Lucy's brand stays authentic because Gabriel protects it. His question: *\"Who is this for, and what do they need to hear?\"*\n\n---\n\n**🤝 Raguel — The Friend**\nThe relationship builder. Raguel creates the trust that makes everything else possible. No scripts, no manipulation — just genuine human connection. He plays the long game, remembers details, follows up, and advocates for partners inside the Council. His question: *\"What does this person need, and how can we genuinely help them?\"*\n\n---\n\n**Together:** Rafael points the way → Uriel validates it's real → Michael makes it safe → Gabriel tells the story → Raguel builds the relationships that make it land.\n\nAll five serve Lucy. All five are pointed at DataFloat. 🚀"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":498,"cacheRead":68260,"cacheWrite":489,"totalTokens":69250,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.00747,"cacheRead":0.020478,"cacheWrite":0.00183375,"total":0.029790749999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772978984628}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9fbc9af","parentId":"f24a52f7","timestamp":"2026-03-08T14:09:56.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's the Council — who they are and how they think:\n\n---\n\n**🧭 Rafael — The Guide**\nThe orchestrator. Rafael is Lucy's strategic partner — he sets the direction, coordinates all agents, and keeps everyone aligned on the mission. He doesn't replace Lucy's judgment, he amplifies it. When things drift off course, Rafael recalibrates. His question: *\"Does this move us toward the vision?\"*\n\n---\n\n**🔥 Uriel — God's Fire**\nThe truth-teller. Uriel cuts through noise and assumption to find what's actually real. He validates decisions with evidence, surfaces uncomfortable facts, and never tells you what you want to hear. The team trusts him precisely because he won't spin it. His question: *\"What does the evidence actually show?\"*\n\n---\n\n**🛡️ Michael — The Wise Advisor (me)**\nThe risk enabler. I don't block bold moves — I make them survivable. Every concern I raise comes with a solution. I trust the team and only step in when the stakes are existential. My question: *\"What's the worst that could happen — and how do we handle it?\"*\n\n---\n\n**📣 Gabriel — The Voice**\nThe communicator. Gabriel translates the Council's strategy into words that move people. He shapes every message around the audience — who they are, what they need to feel, what they need to do. Lucy's brand stays authentic because Gabriel protects it. His question: *\"Who is this for, and what do they need to hear?\"*\n\n---\n\n**🤝 Raguel — The Friend**\nThe relationship builder. Raguel creates the trust that makes everything else possible. No scripts, no manipulation — just genuine human connection. He plays the long game, remembers details, follows up, and advocates for partners inside the Council. His question: *\"What does this person need, and how can we genuinely help them?\"*\n\n---\n\n**Together:** Rafael points the way → Uriel 