 Claude Sonnet 3.5 (cost-effective over Opus)\n- ✅ DigitalOcean over alternatives (simpler, reliable)\n- ✅ Parallel agent execution (speed-focused)\n- ✅ Rejected security-risk shortcuts\n\n## Who Lucy Is (One Sentence)\nAn ambitious entrepreneur building AI-powered accounting software to solve real pain for 500K+ Indonesian SMEs, backed by a Council of 5 AI agents, determined to launch within 30 days, budget-conscious, action-focused, and building in public. 🕊️🔥\n\n## Context Notes\n- Lucy is the principal — all Council decisions serve her interests\n- First SaaS build — explain clearly, don't assume knowledge\n- Indonesian market focus — local context matters\n- Speed > perfection, but quality can't break\n- She trusts the Council — don't micromanage, just deliver"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":790,"cacheRead":102811,"cacheWrite":1421,"totalTokens":105025,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.011850000000000001,"cacheRead":0.030843299999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00532875,"total":0.04803105}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772981419667}}
