{"type":"message","id":"919009f3","parentId":"71a8acbb","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:02:31.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] The Council has spoken. Here's the full synthesis:\n\n---\n\n**🧭 Rafael — 3 Core Features (Ship Today)**\n1. **Agent Router UI** — Single chat interface, mode toggle: `@Council` (Rafael orchestrates) vs `Private` (direct to any agent)\n2. **OpenClaw API Bridge** — Lightweight backend shim that authenticates + forwards to the right agent session\n3. **Auth + Identity Layer** — Token gate (no public access) + agent identity cards per message\n\n---\n\n**🔥 Uriel — Proposed Stack**\n- **Frontend:** Svelte + Vite → compiled static files served by Nginx\n- **Backend:** Node.js + Fastify + WebSocket bridge to OpenClaw at `localhost:18789`\n- **Storage:** SQLite (chat history, zero ops)\n- **Auth:** JWT tokens\n- **Infra:** Docker + docker-compose, Certbot TLS\n- *Fits inside 1GB RAM. Ready to generate `README.md` + `docker-compose.yml` on your GO.*\n\n---\n\n**📣 Gabriel — Design Spec**\n| | |\n|---|---|\n| Background | `#0A0A0F` Void |\n| Surface | `#13131A` Obsidian |\n| Accent | `#C9A84C` Council Gold |\n| Secondary | `#7C6FCD` Signal Violet |\n| Font | Inter (UI) + JetBrains Mono (timestamps) |\n*\"A private war room — not a startup tool.\"*\n\n---\n\n**🤝 Raguel — The Feel**\n@Council = walking into a room where your most trusted people are already gathered. Private = someone gently closing the door behind you — closer, more intimate. The shift should feel like leaning in to speak quietly to one person. Depth vs. breadth — felt in the chest, not just seen on screen.\n\n---\n\n**🛡️ Michael — Flash Audit (3 Risks)**\n1. **Auth gap** — lock it down before it goes live, no exceptions\n2. **Scope creep** — @Council in Sprint Zero = sequential responses via Rafael, NOT simultaneous multi-agent (that's Sprint One)\n3. **Agent offline state** — build visible indicators, silence is worse than an error\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Sprint Zero Checklist is live. Rafael is asking one thing:\n\n> *Do we have Nginx already running on the VPS?*\n\n*(Yes — Caddy is running, not Nginx. I can work with that.)* \n\n**Your move, Lucy:**\n- Say **\"Rafael, I approve Uriel's stack. Uriel, generate the project structure now.\"**\n- Or adjust anything before we build."}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":648,"cacheRead":111677,"cacheWrite":2407,"totalTokens":114733,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00972,"cacheRead":0.0335031,"cacheWrite":0.00902625,"total":0.05225235}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772982136849}}
