{"type":"message","id":"a76a4763","parentId":"c587b049","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:10:46.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Both bugs fixed. Refresh **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**What changed:**\n\n1. **Raw JSON gone** — backend now correctly extracts the actual text from OpenClaw's response format (`result.payloads[0].text`)\n\n2. **All 5 agents respond** — @Council mode now fans out to Rafael, Uriel, Michael, Gabriel, AND Raguel in parallel. Each shows their own \"thinking...\" indicator and posts their own message bubble as they complete\n\n3. **Visual** — each agent's response has a colored left border so you can instantly tell who's speaking\n\nSend a message and you'll see all five respond. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":167,"cacheRead":140545,"cacheWrite":164,"totalTokens":140877,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.002505,"cacheRead":0.0421635,"cacheWrite":0.000615,"total":0.0452865}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772982640016}}
