{"type":"message","id":"7322d79e","parentId":"a4401767","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:11:28.712Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy sent \"hello\" - this seems to be from the control UI (not Telegram based on the message format). Let me respond simply.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Hey Lucy 👋 — Michael here.\n\nAre you testing the Council Room, or is this from Telegram? And did the UI fix work — are all 5 agents responding now?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":95,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":141524,"totalTokens":141622,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.001425,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.530715,"total":0.5321490000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772982681685}}
{"type":"message","id":"f66e0b24","parentId":"7322d79e","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:12:20.942Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_1---b59f16e5-6ff1-4603-b2bd-c43c7bce6a46.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_1---b59f16e5-6ff1-4603-b2bd-c43c7bce6a46.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"74\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"sender\": \"ICat\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 15:12 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ICat (1058350976)\",\n  \"id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"name\": \"ICat\",\n  \"username\": \"icattj\"\n}\n```\n\nhmmm, why private only to Raphael, why why are the chat from council is still here"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1772982740926}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3222d75","parentId":"f66e0b24","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:13:58.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the screenshot, I can see two issues:\n\n1. **Private mode only shows Rafael** - when you click \"Private\", it defaults to Rafael and you can't see the other agents in the sidebar to switch to them (on mobile the sidebar is hidden)\n2. **Council chat history showing in Private mode** - the messages from @Council mode are still visible when switching to Private mode. The chat should clear/separate when switching modes.\n\nAlso I notice Michael is \"thinking\" but hasn't responded yet - that might be a bug too (the \"main\" agent routing).\n\nLet me fix:\n1. **Separate chat histories per mode/agent** - each conversation context should be separate\n\n\n2. **Mobile agent selector** - I need to add a dropdown or selector in the mode bar so users can switch between agents when the sidebar is hidden on mobile\n3. **Clear chat on mode switch** - the conversation should reset or at least visually separate when toggling between Private and Council modes","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Two clear issues from the screenshot:\n\n1. **Private mode stuck on Rafael** — sidebar is hidden on mobile, no way to switch agents\n2. **Chat history bleeds across modes** — Council messages showing in Private\n\nFixing both now:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_fp7F9Bw4NmIKaAQQy5ifhE","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > ~/council-room/frontend/index.html << 'HTMLEOF'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Council Room</title>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<style>\n*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}\n:root{\n  --bg:#0A0A0F;--surface:#13131A;--panel:#1C1C27;--border:#2E2E3E;\n  --gold:#C9A84C;--violet:#7C6FCD;--ivory:#F0EDE8;--ash:#7A7A8C;\n  --sage:#4CAF82;--ember:#E05C5C;\n  --rafael:#7C6FCD;--uriel:#C9A84C;--michael:#4CAF82;--gabriel:#E05C5C;--raguel:#7A8FCD;\n}\nbody{background:var(--bg);color:var(--ivory);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}\n\n/* LOGIN */\n#loginScreen{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:100;background:var(--bg);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}\n.lcard{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem;width:320px;text-align:center}\n.llogo{font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:.6rem}\n.ltitle{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:.25rem}\n.lsub{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--ash);margin-bottom:1.25rem}\n.linput{width:100%;padding:.7rem 1rem;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;color:var(--ivory);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.85rem;outline:none;margin-bottom:.75rem;transition:border-color .2s}\n.linput:focus{border-color:var(--violet)}\n.lbtn{width:100%;padding:.7rem;background:var(--violet);border:none;border-radius:8px;color:#fff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.88rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}\n.lbtn:hover{background:#9f8fe0}\n.lerr{color:var(--ember);font-size:.75rem;margin-top:.5rem}\n\n/* APP */\n#app{display:none;flex-direction:column;height:100vh}\nheader{background:rgba(19,19,26,.97);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 1rem;height:52px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0}\n.logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem}\n.logo-icon{width:26px;height:26px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--violet),var(--gold));border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px}\n.sbadge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.35rem;font-size:.7rem;color:var(--ash);background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:.25rem .6rem;border-radius:20px}\n.dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--sage);animation:pulse 2s infinite}\n@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(76,175,130,.4)}50%{opacity:.7;box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(76,175,130,0)}}\n\n/* LAYOUT */\n.layout{display:flex;flex:1;overflow:hidden}\n.sidebar{width:200px;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--surface);border-right:1px solid var(--border);overflow-y:auto}\n.sb-section{padding:.75rem .6rem .4rem}\n.sb-label{font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--ash);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:0 .4rem;margin-bottom:.35rem}\n.ab{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.55rem;width:100%;padding:.55rem .65rem;background:none;border:none;border-radius:7px;color:var(--ash);cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:.8rem;text-align:left;transition:all .15s;margin-bottom:2px}\n.ab:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);color:var(--ivory)}\n.ab.active{background:rgba(124,111,205,.12);color:var(--ivory)}\n.adot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}\n.aname{font-weight:500;font-size:.8rem;line-height:1.2}\n.arole{font-size:.65rem;color:var(--ash)}\n\n/* CHAT */\n.chat-area{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}\n\n/* MODE BAR */\n.mode-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;padding:.6rem 1rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);flex-shrink:0;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.4rem}\n.mtoggle{display:flex;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:3px;flex-shrink:0}\n.mbtn{padding:.3rem .75rem;border:none;background:none;color:var(--ash);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:500;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}\n.mbtn.active{background:var(--violet);color:#fff}\n.mbtn.cactive{background:var(--gold);color:#0A0A0F}\n\n/* AGENT PICKER (mobile private mode) */\n.agent-picker{display:none;align-items:center;gap:.3rem;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.apick{padding:.28rem .6rem;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--panel);border-radius:20px;color:var(--ash);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:.72rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap}\n.apick:hover{border-color:var(--violet);color:var(--ivory)}\n.apick.active{border-color:var(--violet);background:rgba(124,111,205,.15);color:var(--ivory)}\n\n.active-label{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--ash);white-space:nowrap}\n.active-label strong{color:var(--ivory)}\n\n/* MESSAGES */\n.chat-pane{display:none;flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:1rem;flex-direction:column;gap:.65rem;scroll-behavior:smooth}\n.chat-pane.active{display:flex}\n.chat-pane::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}\n.chat-pane::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);border-radius:2px}\n\n.msg{display:flex;gap:.6rem;animation:mi .22s ease;max-width:90%}\n@keyframes mi{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(7px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}\n.msg.user{align-self:flex-end;flex-direction:row-reverse}\n.mavatar{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:7px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:14px}\n.mbody{flex:1;min-width:0}\n.mmeta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.4rem;margin-bottom:.25rem}\n.mname{font-size:.68rem;font-weight:600}\n.mtime{font-size:.62rem;color:var(--ash);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}\n.mbubble{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:.65rem .9rem;font-size:.84rem;line-height:1.62;color:var(--ivory);white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-word}\n.msg.user .mbubble{background:rgba(124,111,205,.1);border-color:rgba(124,111,205,.2)}\n.mbubble strong,.mbubble b{font-weight:600}\n.mbubble em{font-style:italic;color:#bbb8cc}\n.mbubble code{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.78rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);padding:.1em .3em;border-radius:3px}\n\n.trow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.4rem;padding:.3rem .4rem;color:var(--ash);font-size:.72rem;font-style:italic;animation:mi .2s ease}\n.tdots span{display:inline-block;width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:currentColor;margin:0 1px;animation:td 1.2s infinite}\n.tdots span:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.2s}\n.tdots span:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.4s}\n@keyframes td{0%,80%,100%{transform:scale(.6);opacity:.4}40%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}}\n\n.empty{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--ash);text-align:center;gap:.6rem;padding:2rem}\n.eicon{font-size:2.5rem;opacity:.2}\n.etitle{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--ivory);opacity:.3}\n.esub{font-size:.75rem;max-width:240px;opacity:.4;line-height:1.5}\n\n/* INPUT */\n.input-area{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:.75rem 1rem;background:var(--surface);flex-shrink:0}\n.iwrap{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:.6rem;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:.55rem .65rem;transition:border-color .2s}\n.iwrap:focus-within{border-color:var(--violet)}\n#msgInput{flex:1;background:none;border:none;outline:none;color:var(--ivory);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:.86rem;resize:none;max-height:110px;line-height:1.5}\n#msgInput::placeholder{color:var(--ash)}\n.sbtn{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:7px;border:none;background:var(--violet);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;transition:all .15s}\n.sbtn:hover{background:#9f8fe0}\n.sbtn:disabled{opacity:.4;cursor:not-allowed}\n.sbtn.council{background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg)}\n.ihint{font-size:.66rem;color:var(--ash);margin-top:.35rem;padding:0 .2rem}\n\n@media(min-width:641px){.agent-picker{display:none!important}}\n@media(max-width:640px){\n  .sidebar{display:none}\n  .agent-picker{display:flex}\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div id=\"loginScreen\">\n  <div class=\"lcard\">\n    <div class=\"llogo\">⚡</div>\n    <div class=\"ltitle\">Council Room</div>\n    <div class=\"lsub\">Enter your access token</div>\n    <input type=\"password\" class=\"linput\" id=\"tokenInput\" placeholder=\"Token...\" onkeydown=\"if(event.key==='Enter')login()\">\n    <button class=\"lbtn\" onclick=\"login()\">Enter</button>\n    <div class=\"lerr\" id=\"lerr\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"app\">\n  <header>\n    <div class=\"logo\"><div class=\"logo-icon\">⚡</div>Council Room</div>\n    <div class=\"sbadge\"><div class=\"dot\"></div>5 online</div>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"layout\">\n    <!-- SIDEBAR (desktop) -->\n    <div class=\"sidebar\">\n      <div class=\"sb-section\">\n        <div class=\"sb-label\">Broadcast</div>\n        <button class=\"ab active\" onclick=\"setCouncil()\" id=\"btn-council\">\n          <div class=\"adot\" style=\"background:var(--gold)\"></div>\n          <div><div class=\"aname\" style=\"color:var(--gold)\">@Council</div><div class=\"arole\">All 5 agents</div></div>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sb-section\">\n        <div class=\"sb-label\">Private</div>\n        <button class=\"ab\" onclick=\"setPrivate('rafael')\" id=\"btn-rafael\"><div class=\"adot\" style=\"background:var(--rafael)\"></div><div><div class=\"aname\">🧭 Rafael</div><div class=\"arole\">The Guide</div></div></button>\n        <button class=\"ab\" onclick=\"setPrivate('uriel')\" id=\"btn-uriel\"><div class=\"adot\" style=\"background:var(--uriel)\"></div><div><div class=\"aname\">🔥 Uriel</div><div class=\"arole\">God's Fire</div></div></button>\n        <button class=\"ab\" onclick=\"setPrivate('michael')\" id=\"btn-michael\"><div class=\"adot\" style=\"background:var(--michael)\"></div><div><div class=\"aname\">🛡️ Michael</div><div class=\"arole\">Wise Advisor</div></div></button>\n        <button class=\"ab\" onclick=\"setPrivate('gabriel')\" id=\"btn-gabriel\"><div class=\"adot\" style=\"background:var(--gabriel)\"></div><div><div class=\"aname\">📣 Gabriel</div><div class=\"arole\">The Voice</div></div></button>\n        <button class=\"ab\" onclick=\"setPrivate('raguel')\" id=\"btn-raguel\"><div class=\"adot\" style=\"background:var(--raguel)\"></div><div><div class=\"aname\">🤝 Raguel</div><div class=\"arole\">The Friend</div></div></button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CHAT -->\n    <div class=\"chat-area\">\n      <div class=\"mode-bar\">\n        <div class=\"mtoggle\">\n          <button class=\"mbtn cactive active\" id=\"mCouncil\" onclick=\"setCouncil()\">⚡ @Council</button>\n          <button class=\"mbtn\" id=\"mPrivate\" onclick=\"setPrivate(currentAgent)\">🔒 Private</button>\n        </div>\n        <!-- Mobile agent picker (only shown in private mode) -->\n        <div class=\"agent-picker\" id=\"agentPicker\">\n          <button class=\"apick\" onclick=\"setPrivate('rafael')\" id=\"pick-rafael\">🧭 Rafael</button>\n          <button class=\"apick\" onclick=\"setPrivate('uriel')\" id=\"pick-uriel\">🔥 Uriel</button>\n          <button class=\"apick\" onclick=\"setPrivate('michael')\" id=\"pick-michael\">🛡️ Michael</button>\n          <button class=\"apick\" onclick=\"setPrivate('gabriel')\" id=\"pick-gabriel\">📣 Gabriel</button>\n          <button class=\"apick\" onclick=\"setPrivate('raguel')\" id=\"pick-raguel\">🤝 Raguel</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"active-label\" id=\"activeLabel\">→ <strong>@Council</strong></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- One pane per context -->\n      <div class=\"chat-pane active\" id=\"pane-council\"><div class=\"empty\"><div class=\"eicon\">⚡</div><div class=\"etitle\">@Council</div><div class=\"esub\">All 5 agents will respond to your message.</div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"chat-pane\" id=\"pane-rafael\"><div class=\"empty\"><div class=\"eicon\">🧭</div><div class=\"etitle\">Rafael</div><div class=\"esub\">Private conversation with The Guide.</div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"chat-pane\" id=\"pane-uriel\"><div class=\"empty\"><div class=\"eicon\">🔥</div><div class=\"etitle\">Uriel</div><div class=\"esub\">Private conversation with God's Fire.</div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"chat-pane\" id=\"pane-michael\"><div class=\"empty\"><div class=\"eicon\">🛡️</div><div class=\"etitle\">Michael</div><div class=\"esub\">Private conversation with The Wise Advisor.</div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"chat-pane\" id=\"pane-gabriel\"><div class=\"empty\"><div class=\"eicon\">📣</div><div class=\"etitle\">Gabriel</div><div class=\"esub\">Private conversation with The Voice.</div></div></div>\n      <div class=\"chat-pane\" id=\"pane-raguel\"><div class=\"empty\"><div class=\"eicon\">🤝</div><div class=\"etitle\">Raguel</div><div class=\"esub\">Private conversation with The Friend.</div></div></div>\n\n      <div class=\"input-area\">\n        <div class=\"iwrap\">\n          <textarea id=\"msgInput\" rows=\"1\" placeholder=\"Message the Council...\" onkeydown=\"handleKey(event)\" oninput=\"autoResize(this)\"></textarea>\n          <button class=\"sbtn council\" id=\"sendBtn\" onclick=\"send()\">\n            <svg width=\"15\" height=\"15\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"22\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"11\" y2=\"13\"/><polygon points=\"22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2\"/></svg>\n          </button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ihint\" id=\"ihint\">@Council — all 5 agents respond</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\nconst API = window.location.origin+'/council-api';\nconst WS_URL = API.replace('https://','wss://').replace('http://','ws://')+'/ws';\nconst AGENTS={rafael:{name:'Rafael',emoji:'🧭',role:'The Guide'},uriel:{name:'Uriel',emoji:'🔥',role:\"God's Fire\"},michael:{name:'Michael',emoji:'🛡️',role:'Wise Advisor'},gabriel:{name:'Gabriel',emoji:'📣',role:'The Voice'},raguel:{name:'Raguel',emoji:'🤝',role:'The Friend'}};\nconst COLORS={rafael:'--rafael',uriel:'--uriel',michael:'--michael',gabriel:'--gabriel',raguel:'--raguel'};\n\nlet token=localStorage.getItem('council_token')||'';\nlet mode='council', currentAgent='rafael';\nlet ws=null, thinking={};\n\n// ── AUTH\nasync function login(){\n  const t=document.getElementById('tokenInput').value.trim();\n  if(!t)return;\n  try{const r=await fetch(`${API}/health`,{headers:{'x-council-token':t}});\n    if(r.ok){save(t);}else{document.getElementById('lerr').textContent='Invalid token.';}}\n  catch{save(t);}\n}\nfunction save(t){token=t;localStorage.setItem('council_token',t);document.getElementById('loginScreen').style.display='none';document.getElementById('app').style.display='flex';connectWS();}\nif(token)setTimeout(()=>save(token),50);\n\n// ── WS\nfunction connectWS(){\n  ws=new WebSocket(`${WS_URL}?token=${token}`);\n  ws.onmessage=e=>handle(JSON.parse(e.data));\n  ws.onclose=()=>setTimeout(connectWS,3000);\n  ws.onerror=()=>{};\n}\nfunction handle(d){\n  if(d.type==='thinking'){\n    const pane=mode==='council'?'council':currentAgent;\n    if(!thinking[d.agentId]){thinking[d.agentId]=addThinking(pane,d.agentId);}\n  }else if(d.type==='response'){\n    removeThinking(d.agentId);\n    const pane=mode==='council'?'council':currentAgent;\n    addMsg(pane,'agent',d.agentId,d.response);\n  }else if(d.type==='council_done'||d.type==='error'){\n    Object.keys(thinking).forEach(removeThinking);\n    thinking={};\n    document.getElementById('sendBtn').disabled=false;\n    if(d.type==='error')addSys(mode==='council'?'council':currentAgent,'⚠️ '+d.message);\n  }\n}\n\n// ── MODE\nfunction setCouncil(){\n  mode='council';\n  document.querySelectorAll('.ab').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));\n  document.getElementById('btn-council').classList.add('active');\n  document.getElementById('mCouncil').classList.add('active','cactive');\n  document.getElementById('mPrivate').classList.remove('active');\n  document.getElementById('activeLabel').innerHTML='→ <strong>@Council</strong>';\n  document.getElementById('agentPicker').style.display='none';\n  document.getElementById('sendBtn').className='sbtn council';\n  document.getElementById('ihint').textContent='@Council — all 5 agents respond';\n  document.getElementById('msgInput').placeholder='Message the Council...';\n  showPane('council');\n}\nfunction setPrivate(id){\n  mode='private'; currentAgent=id;\n  const a=AGENTS[id];\n  document.querySelectorAll('.ab').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));\n  document.getElementById('btn-'+id)?.classList.add('active');\n  document.getElementById('mPrivate').classList.add('active');\n  document.getElementById('mCouncil').classList.remove('active','cactive');\n  document.getElementById('activeLabel').innerHTML=`→ <strong>${a.emoji} ${a.name}</strong>`;\n  document.getElementById('agentPicker').style.display='';\n  document.querySelectorAll('.apick').forEach(b=>b.classList.remove('active'));\n  document.getElementById('pick-'+id)?.classList.add('active');\n  document.getElementById('sendBtn').className='sbtn';\n  document.getElementById('ihint').textContent=`Private — ${a.name} (${a.role})`;\n  document.getElementById('msgInput').placeholder=`Message ${a.name}...`;\n  showPane(id);\n}\nfunction showPane(id){\n  document.querySelectorAll('.chat-pane').forEach(p=>p.classList.remove('active'));\n  document.getElementById('pane-'+id).classList.add('active');\n}\n\n// ── SEND\nfunction send(){\n  const inp=document.getElementById('msgInput');\n  const msg=inp.value.trim();\n  if(!msg||!ws||ws.readyState!==1)return;\n  const pane=mode==='council'?'council':currentAgent;\n  addMsg(pane,'user',null,msg);\n  inp.value='';inp.style.height='auto';\n  document.getElementById('sendBtn').disabled=true;\n  document.getElementById('pane-'+pane).querySelector('.empty')?.remove();\n  ws.send(JSON.stringify({mode,agentId:currentAgent,message:msg}));\n}\nfunction handleKey(e){if(e.key==='Enter'&&!e.shiftKey){e.preventDefault();send();}}\nfunction autoResize(el){el.style.height='auto';el.style.height=Math.min(el.scrollHeight,110)+'px';}\n\n// ── RENDER\nfunction t(){return new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US',{hour:'2-digit',minute:'2-digit'});}\nfunction addMsg(pane,from,agentId,text){\n  const p=document.getElementById('pane-'+pane);\n  const isUser=from==='user';\n  const a=agentId?AGENTS[agentId]:null;\n  const cv=agentId?`var(${COLORS[agentId]||'--violet'})`:'var(--gold)';\n  const name=isUser?'Lucy':(a?`${a.emoji} ${a.name}`:'⚡ Council');\n  const abg=isUser?'rgba(124,111,205,.18)':'rgba(255,255,255,.06)';\n  const d=document.createElement('div');\n  d.className='msg'+(isUser?' user':'');\n  if(!isUser)d.style.borderLeft=`2px solid ${cv}`;\n  d.innerHTML=`<div class=\"mavatar\" style=\"background:${abg}\">${isUser?'👤':(a?.emoji||'⚡')}</div><div class=\"mbody\"><div class=\"mmeta\"><span class=\"mname\" style=\"color:${cv}\">${name}</span><span class=\"mtime\">${t()}</span></div><div class=\"mbubble\">${fmt(text)}</div></div>`;\n  p.appendChild(d);p.scrollTop=p.scrollHeight;\n}\nfunction addThinking(pane,agentId){\n  const p=document.getElementById('pane-'+pane);\n  const a=AGENTS[agentId];const cv=`var(${COLORS[agentId]||'--violet'})`;\n  const d=document.createElement('div');d.className='trow';d.id='t-'+agentId;d.style.color=cv;\n  d.innerHTML=`${a?.emoji||'⚡'} <span style=\"font-weight:500\">${a?.name||'?'}</span> is thinking <div class=\"tdots\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>`;\n  p.appendChild(d);p.scrollTop=p.scrollHeight;return d;\n}\nfunction removeThinking(id){document.getElementById('t-'+id)?.remove();delete thinking[id];}\nfunction addSys(pane,txt){const p=document.getElementById('pane-'+pane);const d=document.createElement('div');d.style.cssText='text-align:center;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--ash);padding:.4rem;';d.textContent=txt;p.appendChild(d);}\nfunction fmt(t){return t.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/\\*\\*(.*?)\\*\\*/g,'<strong>$1</strong>').replace(/__(.*?)__/g,'<strong>$1</strong>').replace(/\\*(.*?)\\*/g,'<em>$1</em>').replace(/`(.*?)`/g,'<code>$1</code>').replace(/\\n/g,'<br>');}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\nHTMLEOF\nwc -c ~/council-room/frontend/index.html"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":7546,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":141480,"totalTokens":149029,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.11319,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.53055,"total":0.6437489999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772982740936}}
