{"type":"message","id":"be094d07","parentId":"44c62c76","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:14:08.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Fixed. Hard refresh the page: **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**Two things fixed:**\n\n1. **Private mode now has an agent picker on mobile** — when you tap 🔒 Private, a row of buttons appears: `🧭 Rafael` `🔥 Uriel` `🛡️ Michael` `📣 Gabriel` `🤝 Raguel` — tap any one to switch\n\n2. **Separate chat panes per context** — @Council has its own thread, each Private agent has their own thread. Switching modes no longer bleeds messages across conversations"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":154,"cacheRead":149054,"cacheWrite":94,"totalTokens":149303,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00231,"cacheRead":0.0447162,"cacheWrite":0.0003525,"total":0.0473817}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772982842115}}
