{"type":"message","id":"8fd53c9d","parentId":"f185f3a0","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:23:53.604Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: 4 files]\n[media attached 1/4: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_2---33d72192-5c06-4030-85f5-67ef45d0c9e9.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_2---33d72192-5c06-4030-85f5-67ef45d0c9e9.jpg]\n[media attached 2/4: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_3---90e292ee-1440-4193-8945-e34f563bf519.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_3---90e292ee-1440-4193-8945-e34f563bf519.jpg]\n[media attached 3/4: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_4---be4a2d55-7814-4365-af46-102a641cbbe6.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_4---be4a2d55-7814-4365-af46-102a641cbbe6.jpg]\n[media attached 4/4: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_5---89ec36b0-9cad-4f34-92bd-2590908f45a1.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/openclaw/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_5---89ec36b0-9cad-4f34-92bd-2590908f45a1.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"77\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"sender\": \"ICat\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-08 15:23 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ICat (1058350976)\",\n  \"id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"name\": \"ICat\",\n  \"username\": \"icattj\"\n}\n```\n\nalso make a memory feature like in Gemini, so I can make a new chat but still retail the old one"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"image","data"