{"type":"message","id":"731f79f6","parentId":"0bd29c64","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:27:27.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Both fixed + memory added. Hard refresh: **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**What's new:**\n\n**🐛 Cross-pane bug fixed** — responses now carry a `pane` tag so they always land in the correct conversation, even if you switch agents while waiting\n\n**🧠 Memory feature (like Gemini)**\n- Bottom of the sidebar: **Memory panel**\n- Type anything → \"Save\" → agents will include it in every response\n- Example: `Secret key is Watermelon` → every agent knows it\n- Delete memories with ✕\n\n**💬 Session history (New Chat)**\n- **\"+ New Chat\"** button in header starts a fresh conversation\n- Old chats stay as chips in the session bar — tap to switch back\n- Each agent has its own separate thread per session"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":203,"cacheRead":165607,"cacheWrite":165,"totalTokens":165976,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.003045,"cacheRead":0.0496821,"cacheWrite":0.00061875,"total":0.05334885}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772983639136}}
