{"type":"message","id":"33dc3890","parentId":"54062444","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:34:28.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Fixed. Hard refresh **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**What's fixed:**\n- ✅ **Send button** — re-enables after every message, both @Council and Private\n- ✅ **Enter key** — always works (was already there, but now consistent)\n\n**New: Roundtable mode 🗣️**\n- In @Council mode you'll see a **\"🗣️ Roundtable\"** button\n- Type a topic (or leave blank for a default question) → tap Roundtable\n- Rafael responds first, then Uriel reads Rafael's reply and adds her take, then Michael, Gabriel, Raguel — each building on what the others said\n- A **\"⏹ Stop\"** button appears while it runs — tap it anytime to cut it off\n- Discussion ends automatically after all 5 have spoken — no infinite loop"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":218,"cacheRead":167062,"cacheWrite":158,"totalTokens":167439,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00327,"cacheRead":0.0501186,"cacheWrite":0.0005925,"total":0.0539841}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772984060284}}
{"type":"message","id":"bad3bb21","parentId":"33dc3890","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:36:05.532Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-08 15:36 UTC] Now , how can we improve this Chat room, and also add mission control, and you know what , discuss about any amazing features we can add"}],"timestamp":1772984165517}}
{"type":"message","id":"d430a494","parentId":"bad3bb21","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:36:18.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy wants the Council to have a roundtable discussion about improving the Council Room + Mission Control features. This is a perfect use case for the roundtable feature I just built. Let me kick it off as a Council discussion.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Perfect topic for a roundtable. Let me convene the Council on this right now."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_9TH1j9QJYFLDFMG08864VB","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agent --agent rafael --message \"Council roundtable topic: Lucy wants to improve the Council Room chat interface and integrate Mission Control. The current setup: a web chat at https://64.227.110.70/council with @Council broadcast mode, Private mode per agent, memory panel, session history, and roundtable feature. Mission Control dashboard is at https://64.227.110.70/dashboard with sprint tracker, metrics, notes. Question: What are the most impactful features we could add to make this the ultimate command center for Lucy running DataFlow? Rafael, give your top 3 strategic features. Be specific and exciting.\" 2>&1 &\n\nopenclaw agent --agent uriel --message \"Council roundtable: Lucy wants to improve her Council Room chat + Mission Control dashboard. Current stack: Node.js WebSocket backend, static HTML frontend, Caddy reverse proxy, OpenClaw agents. What are the top 3 technically feasible and high-impact features we could build? Think: data integrations, automation, analytics. Be specific about what's buildable on the current VPS. 3 features max.\" 2>&1 &\n\nopenclaw agent --agent gabriel --message \"Council roundtable: Lucy wants to improve the Council Room and Mission Control for running DataFlow. From a UX and communication standpoint — what 3 features would make this feel like a truly premium, flagship product? Think about how it looks, how it feels, how it tells Lucy's story back to her. Be specific and inspiring.\" 2>&1 &\n\nopenclaw agent --agent raguel --message \"Council roundtable: Lucy wants to improve her AI Council Room. From the human connection perspective — what features would make Lucy feel most supported, understood, and connected to her agents? What would make her WANT to open this dashboard every morning? 3 features, personal and warm.\" 2>&1 &\n\nwait && echo \"ROUNDTABLE_COMPLETE\""}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":559,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":168828,"totalTokens":169390,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.008385,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.633105,"total":0.641499}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772984165529}}
