{"type":"message","id":"bc8210f7","parentId":"43bcda21","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:39:37.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done. Refresh **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**How Roundtable works now:**\n\n1. **Type your topic** in the message box first\n2. Tap **🗣️ Roundtable** — if the box is empty, it flashes gold and says *\"Type your topic first\"*\n3. Rafael → Uriel → Gabriel → Raguel each respond, building on each other\n4. **🛡️ Michael always goes last** — posts a `📋 Roundtable Summary` with key points, any consensus, and one clear next action for you\n5. Hit **⏹ Stop** anytime — Michael will still summarize whatever was discussed before you stopped"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":178,"cacheRead":174210,"cacheWrite":115,"totalTokens":174504,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00267,"cacheRead":0.052263,"cacheWrite":0.00043125,"total":0.05536725}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772984369243}}
{"type":"message","id":"242541a3","parentId":"bc8210f7","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:41:51.571Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-08 15:41 UTC] Let's talk about the feature, I don't want long boring detail, straight to the point, and this is personal , not for sale , no need to add anything like security or such, just so I can monitor all of you, Mission control as well, smoother UI maybe, Keep track token for each hour"}],"timestamp":1772984511556}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0351a67","parentId":"242541a3","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:42:01.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy wants a focused, straight-to-the-point discussion about features to add. She's clear:\n- Personal use, no security/enterprise stuff\n- Monitor the agents\n- Mission Control integration\n- Smoother UI\n- Token tracking per hour\n\nLet me just respond concisely and ask if she wants me to build these or discuss more. Actually she said \"let's talk about\" so maybe she wants to discuss. But given her style (action-oriented, no fluff), I should be direct.\n\nLet me just list what I'm going to build and confirm.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Got it. Here's what I'm building:\n\n**Council Room improvements:**\n- Smoother UI — better animations, cleaner message bubbles, typing feels snappier\n- Token tracker per agent per hour — live counter visible in the UI\n\n**Mission Control merge:**\n- Pull Mission Control into the Council Room as a tab — one URL for everything\n- Sprint progress, days left, bookkeeper count, all visible while you chat\n\n**Agent monitoring:**\n- See which agent is active, last response time, how much they've used this session\n- Simple status bar per agent — green/idle/thinking\n\n---\n\nThat's 5 things. Want me to build all of them now, or pick a starting point?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":302,"cacheRead":15879,"cacheWrite":159112,"totalTokens":175296,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.00453,"cacheRead":0.0047637,"cacheWrite":0.59667,"total":0.6059727}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772984511566}}
