{"type":"message","id":"8d1f5205","parentId":"d012dc05","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:46:52.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Fixed. Refresh **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**What changed:**\n\nThe roundtable now runs as a **background job on the server** — completely independent of your browser. You can:\n- Switch tabs\n- Close the browser\n- Come back later\n\nWhen you reconnect, the UI automatically **replays everything you missed** — all the agent responses that came in while you were away appear instantly.\n\nThe discussion never dies with your connection anymore. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":122,"cacheRead":178362,"cacheWrite":123,"totalTokens":178608,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00183,"cacheRead":0.053508599999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00046125,"total":0.05580285}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772984805964}}
