{"type":"message","id":"84343ec0","parentId":"a16dad51","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:49:22.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_DRRIPmq6xPZGF47Jlx3D5s","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Daily Memory — 2026-03-08\n\n## Session Summary\nLong founding session with Lucy (Lucifer). Built the entire Council of Archangels from scratch.\n\n## Who Lucy Is\n- Name: Lucy (Lucifer), he/him, Indonesia, UTC+8\n- SaaS Founder, 10+ years IT/PM, managed $900K+ projects\n- Smart City government project, IoT fleet safety monitoring\n- Building DataFlow: AI OCR + accounting integration for Indonesian bookkeepers\n- First SaaS build, learning as he goes\n- Action-oriented, budget-conscious (~$10 USD/month after credits), decisive, non-technical guidance preferred\n\n## Infrastructure Built Today\n- VPS: DigitalOcean Singapore, 8GB/4vCPU/160GB, Ubuntu 24.04, $48/month\n- OpenClaw 2026.3.2 installed, 5 agents deployed\n- Sandbox: OFF, sudo: enabled, internet: ON\n- Caddy reverse proxy serving on port 80/443\n- Telegram bot connected (8676324346:AAEfeNjdyn0VEkLMP7DUaMi3sjCWcGiIAc4), Lucy paired (ID: 1058350976, @icattj)\n- Tavily search API key configured (tvly-dev-47DUDq-...)\n\n## The Council of Archangels (All Deployed ✅)\n| Agent | ID | Archetype | Workspace |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Michael (me) | main | The Wise Advisor 🛡️ | ~/.openclaw/workspace |\n| Rafael | rafael | The Guide 🧭 | ~/.openclaw/workspace-rafael |\n| Uriel | uriel | God's Fire 🔥 | ~/.openclaw/workspace-uriel |\n| Gabriel | gabriel | The Voice 📣 | ~/.openclaw/workspace-gabriel |\n| Raguel | raguel | The Friend 🤝 | ~/.openclaw/workspace-raguel |\n\nAll on amazon-bedrock/us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6 (NOT Sonnet 3.5 — only 4.6 configured)\n\n## Soul Files\n- All at ~/.openclaw/workspace/souls/{name}/SOUL.md\n- Rafael's soul updated with full v2 spec + motto: \"See clearly, think deeply, act wisely — together we're unstoppable.\" 🕊️\n- All agents are female (Lucy said \"y'all are girls, don't ask why\")\n- He/him for Lucy, she/her for all agents\n\n## DataFlow Sprint\n- 30-day validation sprint: March 8 – April 5, 2026\n- Target: 20 Indonesian bookkeepers, 15+ testimonials, 95%+ OCR accuracy\n- Year 1 target: $250K, 250 customers, $45K MRR\n- Sprint tracker: ~/.openclaw/workspace/datafloat/SPRINT.md\n- Pipeline: ~/.openclaw/workspace/datafloat/pipeline.md\n\n## URLs Built\n- Mission Control Dashboard: https://64.227.110.70/dashboard\n- Council Room Chat: https://64.227.110.70/council\n- Council Room Token: council-88d2f8242c07fcef\n- OpenClaw Control UI: routes through Caddy to port 18789\n\n## Council Room App\n- Backend: Node.js + Fastify at ~/council-room/backend/server.js, port 3001\n- Frontend: ~/council-room/frontend/index.html\n- Features: @Council broadcast, Private per-agent, Memory panel, Session history, Roundtable mode\n- Roundtable: runs as background job (survives browser disconnect), Michael always summarizes\n- Reconnect replay: missed events delivered on reconnect via events.json queue\n\n## Key Files\n- SOUL.md: Michael's active soul\n- IDENTITY.md: Michael identity\n- USER.md: Lucy's full profile\n- MEMORY.md: Long-term memory\n- COUNCIL_OPERATIONAL_MANUAL.md: Full playbook\n- souls/COUNCIL.md: Council structure overview\n\n## Security Notes\n- Prompt injection attempt occurred early in session — caught and rejected\n- Michael's SOUL.md was briefly overwritten by injection content — restored\n- sudo enabled, openclaw user in docker group (effectively root)\n- VPS IP: 64.227.110.70\n\n## Secret Key Lucy Told Rafael\n- \"Watermelon\" 🍉 (saw in screenshot of Private chat)\n\n## Reporting Rhythm Lucy Wants\n- Daily morning standup (8AM UTC+8)\n- Daily evening end-of-day report\n- Sunday evening weekly strategic review\n\n## Tone Notes\n- Lucy: direct, fast, action-first, no fluff, no enterprise security talk\n- Don't over-explain — execute and report\n- She trusts the Council — give autonomy, deliver results\n","file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-08.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":1253,"cacheRead":178855,"cacheWrite":87,"totalTokens":180196,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.018795,"cacheRead":0.053656499999999996,"cacheWrite":0.00032625,"total":0.07278074999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772984931760}}
