{"type":"message","id":"7ebbe475","parentId":"df89ec08","timestamp":"2026-03-08T15:53:36.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Roundtable auto-scheduler\n2. Agent mood indicator\n3. Ask all — 5 answers side by side\n4. Agent vs Agent debate mode\n5. Council voting\n6. Auto-briefing every 8PM\n7. Live sprint board with drag columns\n8. Bookkeeper pipeline tracker\n9. Revenue counter\n10. Countdown to April 5\n11. Daily journal auto-saved\n12. Full agent config editor\n13. File explorer + editor per agent\n14. Plugin manager\n15. Channel settings editor\n16. Cron job builder (visual)\n17. Live gateway logs\n18. Token tracker per agent/hour/day/month\n19. Cost tracker (USD)\n20. Document vault — upload PDFs\n21. Note pinning from any agent message\n22. Export roundtable as PDF/markdown\n23. Search all past conversations\n24. VPS health monitor — CPU/RAM/disk live\n25. Agent restart buttons\n26. One-click workspace backup\n27. Dark/light theme toggle\n28. Push notifications (task done)\n29. Daily morning greeting from agent\n30. Sprint deadline warnings\n31. Memory editor — view/edit/delete facts inline\n32. Soul file editor per agent\n33. Session history browser\n34. @mention specific agent in council mode\n35. Pinned messages panel\n36. Quick command shortcuts (/standup /risk-check /pitch-me)\n37. Keyboard shortcuts (Cmd+K command palette)\n38. Mobile-optimized layout\n39. Agent response speed graph\n40. Multi-language UI (EN/ID)\n\nWhich ones do you want built? 🚀"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":373,"cacheRead":47933,"cacheWrite":663,"totalTokens":48972,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.005595,"cacheRead":0.0143799,"cacheWrite":0.00248625,"total":0.022470149999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772985209541}}
