{"type":"message","id":"03861eba","parentId":"4ec033c1","timestamp":"2026-03-08T16:15:29.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done. Refresh **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**New roundtable flow:**\n\n1. **🛡️ Michael opens** — breaks down your topic, assigns each agent a specific angle in the right order\n2. **🧭 Rafael** — addresses her assigned angle, can counter Michael\n3. **🔥 Uriel** — responds to her angle + can push back on Rafael\n4. **📣 Gabriel** — builds on or counters anyone before her\n5. **🤝 Raguel** — same, plus the human perspective\n6. **🛡️ Michael closes** — synthesizes everything, calls out disagreements, gives you ONE clear decision\n\nEvery agent reads the full conversation before responding — so it's an actual debate, not parallel monologues. Try it with the money question 👇"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":205,"cacheRead":88010,"cacheWrite":103,"totalTokens":88319,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.003075,"cacheRead":0.026403,"cacheWrite":0.00038625,"total":0.02986725}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772986523168}}
