{"type":"message","id":"f15b3e93","parentId":"95e0d879","timestamp":"2026-03-08T16:23:09.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The agent call seems to be hanging. Let me try a different approach - run the agents directly via the openclaw CLI differently, or just do it without the python parsing. Let me check if openclaw agent command is taking too long.\n\nActually, the roundtable via Telegram is going to be slow because I'm running agents sequentially from the CLI. Let me suggest Lucy use the Council Room UI for roundtables (which runs in background) and just give her Michael's opening here, then tell her to go to the Council Room for the full discussion.\n\nLet me kill this hanging process and try a simpler approach.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_krE9pj3s2cJjOcwUvaotFp","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"grand-nexus"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":217,"cacheRead":90940,"cacheWrite":87,"totalTokens":91245,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.003255,"cacheRead":0.027281999999999997,"cacheWrite":0.00032625,"total":0.030866249999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772986984363}}
