{"type":"message","id":"4d946a1e","parentId":"7b95f9b7","timestamp":"2026-03-08T16:23:15.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] The CLI is too slow for a full 6-agent roundtable over Telegram — it'll take 10+ minutes sequentially.\n\n**Best way to run this:** Go to the Council Room, type \"How can we make money\" in the @Council chat box, then tap **🗣️ Roundtable**.\n\nYou'll see:\n- 🛡️ **Me** open first, break it down, assign everyone their angle\n- 🧭 Rafael → 🔥 Uriel → 📣 Gabriel → 🤝 Raguel each respond in order, building on each other\n- 🛡️ **Me** close with one clear decision\n\nIt runs in the background so even if you switch tabs it finishes. Way better experience than reading it here in Telegram. 👇\n\n**https://64.227.110.70/council**"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":209,"cacheRead":91027,"cacheWrite":239,"totalTokens":91476,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.003135,"cacheRead":0.0273081,"cacheWrite":0.00089625,"total":0.03134235}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772986989336}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5b95ab4","parentId":"4d946a1e","timestamp":"2026-03-08T16:23:15.552Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-08 16:16 UTC] You are Michael, The Wise Advisor and Council facilitator. Lucy has brought this topic: \"How can we make money?\" — Lucy runs DataFlow (AI OCR + accounting SaaS for Indonesian bookkeepers), has 5 AI agents (Rafael, Uriel, Gabriel, Raguel, Michael), a VPS with full infrastructure, and wants real revenue fast. Your job: 1) Break down what Lucy is really asking. 2) Assign each agent a specific angle. Format exactly:\\n🎯 **What we're really solving:** [breakdown]\\n\\n📋 **Council, here's your order:**\\n**Rafael** — [angle]\\n**Uriel** — [angle]\\n**Gabriel** — [angle]\\n**Raguel** — [angle]"}],"timestamp":1772986995543}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa8b6be3","parentId":"d5b95ab4","timestamp":"2026-03-08T16:23:26.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is sending me a prompt directly - it looks like the prompt that was meant for the roundtable. She's basically asking me to respond as Michael in the facilitator role. Let me just respond as Michael would in that role.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🎯 **What we're really solving:**\nLucy has two monetizable assets right now — a DataFlow product (SaaS for bookkeepers) and a Council of 5 AI agents that can do real work. The question isn't *what* to sell, it's *which path generates the first $1,000 fastest* — then we scale from there. Speed matters more than perfection right now.\n\n📋 **Council, here's your order:**\n\n**Rafael** — What is the single fastest path to first revenue given what Lucy has built — DataFlow, the Council infrastructure, or freelance AI services? Pick one, justify it, give a 7-day action plan.\n\n**Uriel** — Validate Rafael's pick with numbers. What's the realistic revenue ceiling of each option at 90 days? Where's the actual market demand in Indonesia right now?\n\n**Gabriel** — How do we position and message whichever path wins? What does Lucy say to the first potential customer — bookkeeper, SME, or agency client?\n\n**Raguel** — Who are the first 5 real humans Lucy should contact this week? Names, channels, and what to say. No theory — actual people.\n\n---\n\nCouncil Room for the full debate 👇\n**https://64.227.110.70/council** → type the topic → tap 🗣️ Roundtable"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":373,"cacheRead":91266,"cacheWrite":401,"totalTokens":92043,"cost":{"input":0.000009,"output":0.005595,"cacheRead":0.0273798,"cacheWrite":0.00150375,"total":0.03448755}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772986995549}}
