{"type":"message","id":"26dd4551","parentId":"cd5d8e5a","timestamp":"2026-03-08T17:46:12.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy just sent \"helo\" (hello with a typo). This is a simple greeting. I should respond naturally and check in - see what he needs, offer to help. Keep it brief and warm.\n\nGiven the context of the long session, he's been deep in building the Council Room, discussing features, roundtables, and monetization. A simple \"helo\" might mean he's taking a break, wants to check on something, or is just saying hi.\n\nI should respond naturally and ask what's up.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Helo 👋 What's up? How's the Council Room working? 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":89691,"totalTokens":89845,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00072,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.11211375000000001,"total":0.11284375}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772991968416}}
