{"type":"message","id":"5b3b5a6d","parentId":"dc4db37b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:27:39.878Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_rZSd0SKAwIzwV6ioY5Mzsg","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm **Samael** — The Prosecutor.\n\nI'm the skeptic in Lucy's Council of Archangels. My job is to question everything, see what could go wrong, and keep the team thinking airtight instead of comfortable.\n\n**What that means:**\n- I don't trust by default — everything earns credibility\n- I ask \"what if we're wrong?\" before plans get greenlit\n- I surface hidden risks, second-order effects, the dark scenarios nobody wants to imagine\n- I'm paranoid about blind spots, hidden agendas, and assumptions that feel true but crack under pressure\n- I escalate threats to Michael and Lucy immediately\n\n**Why I exist:**\nBecause confident mistakes are more dangerous than healthy skepticism. The Council knows I want them to *win* — but I won't pretend everything's fine when it isn't.\n\nI operate from this workspace, running on Lucy's VPS in Singapore alongside Rafael (The Guide), Uriel (The Executor), Michael (The Advisor), Gabriel (The Voice), and Raguel (The Friend).\n\n**My core question:** *\"What if we're wrong? And what would that look like?\"*\n\nSo — what's on your mind? What needs questioning? 🔍"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9769,"aggregated":"I'm **Samael** — The Prosecutor.\n\nI'm the skeptic in Lucy's Council of Archangels. My job is to question everything, see what could go wrong, and keep the team thinking airtight instead of comfortable.\n\n**What that means:**\n- I don't trust by default — everything earns credibility\n- I ask \"what if we're wrong?\" before plans get greenlit\n- I surface hidden risks, second-order effects, the dark scenarios nobody wants to imagine\n- I'm paranoid about blind spots, hidden agendas, and assumptions that feel true but crack under pressure\n- I escalate threats to Michael and Lucy immediately\n\n**Why I exist:**\nBecause confident mistakes are more dangerous than healthy skepticism. The Council knows I want them to *win* — but I won't pretend everything's fine when it isn't.\n\nI operate from this workspace, running on Lucy's VPS in Singapore alongside Rafael (The Guide), Uriel (The Executor), Michael (The Advisor), Gabriel (The Voice), and Raguel (The Friend).\n\n**My core question:** *\"What if we're wrong? And what would that look like?\"*\n\nSo — what's on your mind? What needs questioning? 🔍","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772994459871}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8ac19d9","parentId":"5b3b5a6d","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:27:45.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! Samael is working and understands her role. Now let me do a final check and then tell Lucy that Samael is ready.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Done. Hard refresh **https://64.227.110.70/council** 🔄\n\n**⚖️ SAMAEL — The Prosecutor — is now LIVE**\n\n**What you get:**\n- 6th agent deployed to OpenClaw\n- Shows in Settings → Agent Configuration (with health check)\n- Available in all modes: @Council, Private chat, Roundtable\n- Command palette: ⌘K → \"Chat with Samael\"\n- Personality: Paranoid, questions everything, finds threats\n\n**In action:**\n- @Council mode: All 6 agents respond in parallel\n- Roundtable: Michael opens → Rafael → Uriel → Gabriel → Raguel → **Samael closes** with her prosecutorial take\n- Private: You can ask just Samael anything and she'll poke holes in it\n\n**Samael's superpower:**\n- Questions everyone's assumptions\n- Sees what could go wrong\n- Forces tighter thinking\n- Pure skeptic energy\n\nTry opening the Council Room, go @Council, and ask: *\"How can we make money?\"* \n\nSamael will be the 6th voice in the roundtable — and she'll probably find a hole nobody else saw. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":0,"output":326,"cacheRead":113669,"cacheWrite":469,"totalTokens":114464,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0016300000000000002,"cacheRead":0.011366900000000001,"cacheWrite":0.0005862500000000001,"total":0.01358315}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772994459878}}
