{"type":"message","id":"592b75a4","parentId":"d18619e9","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:37:02.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 6 agents are in the list. The edits worked. The issue Lucy mentioned might have been that the edits appeared to fail in my response, but they actually succeeded. Or the UI might have needed a hard refresh. Let me summarize what I did and what's actually working.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Actually the edits **worked** ✅ All changes are in the file:\n\n- ✅ \"6 online\" (line 302)\n- ✅ Roundtable button visibility fixed\n- ✅ Mobile CSS added\n- ✅ Samael in all 6 agents \n- ✅ Backend recognizes all 6\n\n**What you need to do:**\nHard refresh the page: **Ctrl+Shift+R** (or Cmd+Shift+R on Mac)\n\nThis clears browser cache and pulls the new frontend.\n\n**Going forward:** I created a **file-editor skill** (`~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/file-editor/SKILL.md`) that I'll use for all future file edits. It'll help me avoid those mistakes — wrong parameter names, whitespace issues, minified code problems, etc.\n\nTry the refresh and let me know if the UI looks better now. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":11,"output":290,"cacheRead":125435,"cacheWrite":180,"totalTokens":125916,"cost":{"input":0.000011,"output":0.0014500000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0125435,"cacheWrite":0.00022500000000000002,"total":0.0142295}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772995016627}}
