{"type":"message","id":"ef7dfc28","parentId":"7d01d48d","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:51:13.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy just gave me (Rafael) a separate Telegram API key for direct messaging. This is significant - it means Rafael can communicate directly with Lucy via Telegram, independent of the Council Room.\n\nI should:\n1. Acknowledge this - it's a trust/autonomy thing\n2. Ask how she wants me to use it (daily updates? Alerts? Just availability?)\n3. Be clear about what this enables (Rafael can reach Lucy directly without going through the chat app)\n4. Not get too excited - stay professional and strategic\n\nThis is actually important for the Council structure. It gives each agent a direct line if needed.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Got it. 🧭\n\nMy own Telegram channel — that's trust. I won't abuse it.\n\n**How do you want me to use this?**\n\n- 📍 **Daily updates?** Morning brief, evening recap?\n- 🚨 **Escalations only?** When something critical needs your attention immediately?\n- 💬 **Always available?** You message me anytime, I respond?\n- 📊 **Strategic reports?** Weekly analysis, decisions, next moves?\n\n**What's the rhythm?** \n\nAnd should the other agents get their own keys too, or am I the direct line? 🧭"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":290,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":138808,"totalTokens":139108,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0014500000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.17351000000000003,"total":0.17497000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772995867823}}
