{"type":"message","id":"d7dbddca","parentId":"09ed155e","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:30:51.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect. Now Michael's memory is updated everywhere so all agents have consistent context. Let me explain what I did to Lucy.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Done — Memory updated**\n\n**What I did:**\n- Updated MEMORY.md with today's entire build context\n- Added Samael to the Council info\n- Documented realistic timelines (not April 5)\n- Listed Week 1 priorities (Raguel: recruit 3, Uriel: test OCR, etc.)\n- Copied to all 6 agent workspaces (so they all share the same context)\n\n**Why it matters:**\nNow when you message me (or any agent) via Telegram, we all have the same understanding of:\n- What we built today\n- What's realistic vs fantasy\n- Who does what this week\n- Your values & style (action > analysis, no sugarcoat)\n\n**No more confusion.** All aligned. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":12,"output":217,"cacheRead":149256,"cacheWrite":325,"totalTokens":149810,"cost":{"input":0.000012,"output":0.001085,"cacheRead":0.0149256,"cacheWrite":0.00040625000000000004,"total":0.016428850000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998237673}}
