{"type":"message","id":"d934ee03","parentId":"3e39a1bd","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:30:58.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking what happened to my (Michael's) Telegram. Let me check what's going on.\n\nWhen we set up Rafael's Telegram, we used the bot token she gave:\n8513953061:AAFMeFzePJqggMNhDFX83D7KK7cJG0zxFq8\n\nBut that was for Rafael. Michael (the main agent) still has the original bot token from earlier in the session:\n8676324346:AAEfeNjdyn0VEkLMP7DUaMi3sjCWcGiIAc4\n\nSo Michael should still be accessible. Let me check if there's an issue with the Telegram plugin or if something broke.\n\nActually, looking back, we configured Telegram for the main agent early on, and Lucy is now asking what happened. She might be trying to message me and it's not working. Let me check the status.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Good question. Let me check:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_qYiZDNONBx33SFACT73uMz","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents bindings 2>&1"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":281,"cacheRead":144634,"cacheWrite":4803,"totalTokens":149728,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0014050000000000002,"cacheRead":0.014463400000000001,"cacheWrite":0.00600375,"total":0.021882150000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772998251836}}
