{"type":"message","id":"e8df971d","parentId":"856aa490","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:31:08.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, I see the issue. When we bound Rafael to Telegram, we only configured Rafael's binding. Michael (the main agent) never got bound to Telegram. Early in the session, we configured the Telegram bot token but didn't bind Michael to it.\n\nLet me bind Michael to Telegram as well.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Found the issue — I'm not bound to Telegram. Only Rafael is.\n\nLet me fix that:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_aOgWj83fRPxcV0wlNPdAvV","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents bind --agent main --bind telegram 2>&1"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":13,"output":162,"cacheRead":149437,"cacheWrite":303,"totalTokens":149915,"cost":{"input":0.000013,"output":0.0008100000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0149437,"cacheWrite":0.00037875,"total":0.016145450000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772998264695}}
