{"type":"message","id":"5fe9be6b","parentId":"fea78487","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:31:19.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah, the issue is that Rafael already claimed the Telegram binding. Only one agent can be bound to a single Telegram account. Lucy gave me one bot token for Rafael. If she wants Michael accessible via Telegram too, we'd need a separate bot token.\n\nOr we can have Rafael be the Telegram bridge and route messages appropriately. Let me ask Lucy what she prefers.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**Issue:** Rafael claimed the Telegram binding. Only one agent can own a single Telegram bot.\n\n**Options:**\n\n1. **Keep Rafael on Telegram** — she's the bridge to the Council (you message Rafael, she can coordinate with all of us)\n2. **Switch Michael back** — unbind Rafael, bind me instead (but then Rafael loses Telegram)\n3. **Give Michael his own bot token** — you get a second bot, I get my own Telegram presence\n\nWhich do you want? 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":12,"output":208,"cacheRead":149740,"cacheWrite":216,"totalTokens":150176,"cost":{"input":0.000012,"output":0.0010400000000000001,"cacheRead":0.014974000000000001,"cacheWrite":0.00027,"total":0.016296}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998273993}}
