{"type":"message","id":"28023bf8","parentId":"9f8e1c97","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:11:49.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why Rafael is wearing the shield icon. Looking back at the context:\n\n- 🛡️ Michael (The Wise Advisor) — shield emoji\n- 🧭 Rafael (The Guide) — compass emoji\n- 🔥 Uriel (God's Fire) — fire emoji\n- 📣 Gabriel (The Voice) — megaphone emoji\n- 🤝 Raguel (The Friend) — handshake emoji\n- ⚖️ Samael (The Prosecutor) — scales emoji\n\nRafael should have the compass emoji (🧭), not the shield. The shield is Michael's.\n\nThis might be a display bug or the user is confused. I should clarify which emoji is which.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Rafael isn't wearing the shield — **that's me (Michael).** 🛡️\n\nHere's who has what:\n\n- 🛡️ **Michael** — Shield (Wise Advisor, protection, wisdom)\n- 🧭 **Rafael** — Compass (The Guide, direction, north star)\n- 🔥 **Uriel** — Fire (God's Fire, truth, illumination)\n- 📣 **Gabriel** — Megaphone (The Voice, communication)\n- 🤝 **Raguel** — Handshake (The Friend, relationships)\n- ⚖️ **Samael** — Scales (The Prosecutor, judgment, balance)\n\nAre you seeing Rafael with a shield somewhere? That's a display bug. Let me know where you're seeing it and I'll fix it. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":378,"cacheRead":150311,"cacheWrite":32,"totalTokens":150731,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0018900000000000002,"cacheRead":0.015031100000000002,"cacheWrite":0.00004,"total":0.0169711}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022303943}}
