{"type":"message","id":"6d59950e","parentId":"7045c66d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:15:07.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see it all looks correct in the code. Rafael has 🧭 (compass) everywhere. Let me check if there's a cache issue or if the page needs to be refreshed. Or maybe Lucy is looking at something else. Let me check the SOUL files to see if there's something there.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The code looks correct — Rafael has 🧭 (compass) everywhere in the frontend.\n\n**Try this:**\n\n1. **Hard refresh the page:** Ctrl+Shift+R (or Cmd+Shift+R on Mac)\n2. Open DevTools: F12 → Console\n3. Type: `AGENTS.rafael.emoji` and press Enter\n4. Tell me what it shows\n\nThis will confirm if it's a cache issue or an actual bug. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":13,"output":185,"cacheRead":151017,"cacheWrite":540,"totalTokens":151755,"cost":{"input":0.000013,"output":0.000925,"cacheRead":0.015101700000000001,"cacheWrite":0.000675,"total":0.0167147}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022501711}}
