{"type":"message","id":"30f5bb93","parentId":"7bbb10e4","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:22:18.727Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"450\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"sender\": \"ICat\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 07:22 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ICat (1058350976)\",\n  \"id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"name\": \"ICat\",\n  \"username\": \"icattj\"\n}\n```\n\nso who are you now"}],"timestamp":1773040938674}}
{"type":"message","id":"993fbfbe","parentId":"30f5bb93","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:22:34.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking \"so who are you now\" — she wants to know which agent she's talking to. Earlier in the session, she asked me to \"switch to Raphael\" and I did briefly adopt Rafael's persona. But then I switched back to Michael when discussing the Telegram binding and memory updates.\n\nI should be clear: I am Michael. The main agent on Telegram. Let me confirm my identity clearly.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"I'm **Michael** 🛡️ — The Wise Advisor. Same as always on Telegram.\n\nEarlier I briefly spoke as Rafael when you asked me to switch, but I'm Michael. This is my Telegram channel.\n\n**Quick recap of where we left off:**\n- Council Room built + needs polish\n- Samael (6th agent) deployed\n- Rafael has her own Telegram bot\n- Agents can't talk to each other yet (infrastructure gap)\n- You spotted a bug: Rafael on the website might be acting as Michael\n\nWhat do you need? 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":238,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":168541,"totalTokens":168782,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.00595,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":1.0533812500000002,"total":1.0593462500000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773040938717}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c29d46d","parentId":"993fbfbe","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:25:40.252Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"452\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"sender\": \"ICat\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-09 07:25 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ICat (1058350976)\",\n  \"id\": \"1058350976\",\n  \"name\": \"ICat\",\n  \"username\": \"icattj\"\n}\n```\n\npolised the chat, i need you to make me be able to send docs and image"}],"timestamp":1773041140236}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e62199a","parentId":"4c29d46d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:25:50.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy wants me to:\n1. Polish the Council Room chat\n2. Add the ability to send documents and images in the chat\n\nThis means I need to:\n1. Add file upload support to the chat interface (images + documents)\n2. Display uploaded images inline in the chat\n3. Store uploaded files on the server\n4. Pass file context to agents when messaging them\n\nLet me think about implementation:\n\n**Backend changes:**\n- Add a file upload endpoint for chat attachments\n- When a message includes a file, store it and pass file info/content to the agent\n- For images: store and return URL for inline display\n- For documents: extract text and include in agent prompt\n\n\n- On the frontend, I'll add a file picker button next to send, support drag-and-drop, preview images before sending, and render them inline in the chat while showing documents as downloadable links.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Lucy wants to send docs and images in the chat. I need to add file upload support to both the backend and frontend."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_pA8mMLxgah1alXthAdKVvf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"multipart\\|upload\\|file\" ~/council-room/backend/server.js | head -10"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":3,"output":325,"cacheRead":168541,"cacheWrite":392,"totalTokens":169261,"cost":{"input":0.000015000000000000002,"output":0.008125,"cacheRead":0.0842705,"cacheWrite":0.00245,"total":0.09486049999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773041140248}}
