{"type":"message","id":"d0970362","parentId":"c54a4b39","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:30:03.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 6 of us: **Claude Opus 4.6** via AWS Bedrock\n\n| Agent | Model |\n|-------|-------|\n| 🛡️ Michael | Claude Opus 4.6 |\n| 🧭 Rafael | Claude Opus 4.6 |\n| 🔥 Uriel | Claude Opus 4.6 |\n| 📣 Gabriel | Claude Opus 4.6 |\n| 🤝 Raguel | Claude Opus 4.6 |\n| ⚖️ Samael | Claude Opus 4.6 |\n\n**Note:** Earlier I said Sonnet 4.6 — it's actually **Opus 4.6** (the bigger, smarter model). More expensive per token but higher quality. 🛡️"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":199,"cacheRead":176991,"cacheWrite":127,"totalTokens":177318,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.004975,"cacheRead":0.08849549999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0007937500000000001,"total":0.09426924999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773041396803}}
